text: Fiona Johnston (born 3 February 1966) is a British rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:British female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Morpeth, Northumberland Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in rowing Category:Commonwealth Games silver medallists for England Category:Rowers at the 1986 Commonwealth Games
